abstract: >-
  Zara is a persistent, self-improving AI engineering partner built on the
  Model Context Protocol. Features multi-agent orchestration (10 agents),
  3-layer cognitive memory with semantic embeddings, 132-signal adaptive
  skill routing, outcome-weighted reflection loops, and empathetic
  leadership coordination. Designed for developers who want an AI that
  remembers, learns, and grows with them.
